{"tid":1856024,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一百萬人家中工作/停工就每日慳一百萬個口罩","createTime":"2020-02-01T11:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T17:59:49.000Z","uid":45442,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"81a9dfb034bda1d8919cf0d3564055d6e61fd5fb","tid":1856024,"uid":45442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"二百萬人唔洗出去返工就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">每日慳二百萬個口罩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n全港口罩生產谷到24/7，每月生產量都唔過200萬個<br />\n你一日既勞動人口都用晒喇<br />\n<br />\n林鄭一星期前去函國務院要求口罩供應，人地係咪<span style=\"font-size: large;\">已讀不回</span>你？？<br />\n現時市面全部口罩都係私人市場批貨返嚟買，政府話facilitate 通關=做左嘢？？？<br />\n<br />\n現時香港80% 口罩貨源來自中国<br />\n就算中国可以加大產能到一日一億個口罩 (現時一日都唔夠二千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n都唔夠十四億人，我再同你cut 到只計城市勞動人口<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">九億，一人一日一個</span>(根據經濟學人智庫資料)<br />\n<br />\n有無記者可以問下政府識唔識計呢啲數？<br />\n雖然好多個零但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只係減數嚟咋</span></span>"},{"pid":"e370db6f0107c50d4a84a1d28a19efd8876d2cf4","tid":1856024,"uid":70417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"唔係你以為公務員點解home office<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc781bf5995f982deab9309daa8f963265ae1f7","tid":1856024,"uid":45442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e370db6f0107c50d4a84a1d28a19efd8876d2cf4","tid":1856024,"uid":70417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"唔係你以為公務員點解home office<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:09:27.000Z","msg":"咁係咪應該全港home office?"},{"pid":"51543cf0147fab3d91a5740013cd0407e24f5d98","tid":1856024,"uid":212763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bc781bf5995f982deab9309daa8f963265ae1f7","tid":1856024,"uid":45442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e370db6f01